data.description: You are not going to want to miss this beautiful property situated in the Maysville LSD!  Very nicely maintained 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bath home with a spacious living room, open kitchen/dining area and a large office that could also be utilized as a 4th bedroom.  The downstairs has a large wood working area complete with work benches and radial arm saw/air filtration system that conveys.  Recreation/family room has bar area.  200 amp service.  Storage/work shed conveys  Refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, washer, dryer, 92'' TV with speakers and receiver, gazebo on deck, Nest Security system all convey. Located near shopping, dining, Eaglestick Golf Club, and Maysville Schools
